Baiklah.

00:11:07.030 --> 00:11:08.820
Heng, berikan segalanya esok.

00:11:20.300 --> 00:11:21.140
Ayuh.

00:11:21.150 --> 00:11:22.150
Adakah anda pernah melihatnya sebelum ini?

00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:23.870
- Tidak.
- Bagus.

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:25.680
Berikan segalanya.

00:11:26.690 --> 00:11:27.680
Mereka berada di peringkat akhir.

00:11:41.380 --> 00:11:42.360
Cik Xu.

00:11:42.440 --> 00:11:45.120
(Penunggang misteri
yang mewakili penganjur.)

00:11:45.120 --> 00:11:46.390
