"Penunggang Changyi" pertama

00:12:04.870 --> 00:12:06.960
"Berlumba dengan Angin".

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:07.870
Peringkat akhir

00:12:07.870 --> 00:12:09.980
mulakan sekarang.

00:12:12.610 --> 00:12:14.840
Penunggang, ambil kedudukan anda.

00:12:15.060 --> 00:12:15.910
Ayuh!

00:12:15.910 --> 00:12:17.550
Selamatkan pelana anda.

00:12:20.690 --> 00:12:22.240
Bunyi gendang tiga kali.

